{"tid":1488313,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"大家真係唔好再follow個大波madam啦","createTime":"2019-08-19T14:55:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-19T15:08:31.000Z","uid":291448,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"97e875fbcde0430c8129ed26e5a812f859cb9cca","tid":1488313,"uid":291448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T14:55:58.000Z","msg":"大家係咪痴左線？成個阿嬸樣嘅Madam只不過係有對奶喺度大家就精蟲上晒腦 諗都唔諗就去follow佢<br />\n大波madam原本IG粉絲人數<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ESECpYD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FESECpYD.png&h=3b7c7f49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家IG粉絲人數<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hNah9qJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhNah9qJ.png&h=424f4799&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nOn撚9 足足多咗好多倍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大家要<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">記得佢係madam黎 佢可以隨時將呢個粉絲人數list交俾警方 然後逐個捉</span></span> 咁到時大家就仆街啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n請大家停一停 諗一諗 唔好上釣  你一個follow隨時會惹禍上身 要J就J其他靚女或者AV女優啦 淨係個樣同身材都好過個Madam<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />都唔知個madam有咩吸引 除咗對奶之外 咁都J得落真係好重口味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">要follow就follow我個IG<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5EkxYmk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5EkxYmk.png&h=df79b88b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"777ddf7cef3625d01ddde5aab3af7d46bfb0910d","tid":1488313,"uid":241244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T14:56:31.000Z","msg":"（整合） 818之後仲有行動㗎我地！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1487938\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1487938</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n普教中！！！救下香港嘅下一代！！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1475548\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1475548</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"3b5787b5385a5a288c0216ef0ddaa5b28bc58058","tid":1488313,"uid":291448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T14:56:39.000Z","msg":"回頭是岸 各位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"890448dcb67beebd521b2f7dcfffafd2126b29a2","tid":1488313,"uid":291448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T14:57:15.000Z","msg":"要J就J其他嘢"},{"pid":"b9bb8bedb613a3c4ded992006c7053f6ce6e8902","tid":1488313,"uid":291448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T14:58:07.000Z","msg":"因為咸濕而前功盡廢係一件好on9嘅事黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4d686f3e184bb43880f692b73c049371c476d28","tid":1488313,"uid":147485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T14:58:10.000Z","msg":"其實會唔會係班警犬自己follow<br />\n警賊3萬 有2萬幾狗公 好似好合理<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"066f2e0482fe43d21d6cde88691bf9662bad0049","tid":1488313,"uid":291448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f4d686f3e184bb43880f692b73c049371c476d28","tid":1488313,"uid":147485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T14:58:10.000Z","msg":"其實會唔會係班警犬自己follow<br />\n警賊3萬 有2萬幾狗公 好似好合理<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T15:0